            <h6 style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin: 0;">v1.7.0 <span class="lp-badge lp-badge-success" style="font-size: 9px; padding: 2px 6px;">Latest Release</span></h6>
            <span style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted);">July 13, 2026</span>
