          <p style="font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 8px;">
            Added OpenClaw AI Copilot Floating assistant, Nginx Reverse Proxy Docker Mapper, PHP Pool Configuration Manager, Database Visual Explorer/Console, WhatsApp Alerting (Baileys), Service Watchdog Auto-Healer, Visual Audit Log Dashboard, Security Advisor (One-Click Fix), Multi-Cloud S3 Backups, Terminal AI Troubleshooting, and Git Webhook Auto-Build pipelines.
          </p>
